        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the house of Joab, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "or, as it should rather be rendered, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Beth-joab, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "for the writer is not speaking of a family, but of a place. The people of those towns, and the Manahethites, and the Zorites, were all the descendants of this Salma, the son of Caleb. So that, it appears, he had a very numerous posterity.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
