  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The sons of Salma,.... Another son of the younger Caleb, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 2:50",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " whose sons were Bethlehem, the inhabitants of the place, at least many of them, of which he was prince, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 2:51",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and the Netophathite; the inhabitants of Netophah, a place in the tribe of Judah, mentioned along with Bethlehem, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Nehemiah 7:26",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " these sprung from Salma: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Ataroth, the house of Joab; Ataroth seems to be the name of a place in the tribe of Judah, where the family of Joab lived, the inhabitants of which were the descendants of Salma: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and half of the Manahethites; the other half of the inhabitants of Manahath, see 1 Chronicles 2:52, ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and half of the Manahethites; the other half of the inhabitants of Manahath, see ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1 Chronicles 2:52",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ", ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the Zorites; part also of them, called Zareathites, 1 Chronicles 2:53. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "the Zorites; part also of them, called Zareathites, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
